// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mlGcWR random domino square tiling int, 2023 by jt
// integer version of
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/ctdyWl random domino square tiling

// Tiling of randomly (horizontally/vertically) aligned domino tiles
// (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Domino_tiling)
// with dominos merged into squares across tile boundaries and inside tiles.
// Integer version (only final coloring float).

// tags: random, tiling, squares, tesselation, merge, combine, align, domino, adjacent

// The MIT License
